---
title: Beef and Potato Kheema Naans with North Indian spices and garlic yoghurt
description: Kheema naan is a popular dish in Indian cuisine that consists of spiced minced meat (usually lamb) stuffed in a golden fluffy naan bread. In this variation, there's beef mince, potatoes, and a refreshing and zingy salad on the side.
